- **If the SessionStart banner shows host X with role R, you ARE on X.** Any ssh to a name that resolves to X (alias from the table, mDNS `<host>.local`, Tailscale FQDN, Tailscale IP) is a bug. Run locally. If the banner has aged out of context mid-session and you're unsure, run `claude-host` (~/.local/bin/claude-host); it prints role + hostname + Tailscale name + a "don't ssh here" reminder in one line.
