Han's private monorepo `tieubao/ops-toolkit` (`~/workspace/tieubao/ops-toolkit/`) is the personal-tools gradient: matured under `tools/`, scratch under `experiments/`. Lifecycle: experiment → harden to `tools/` OR distill to public `tieubao/til`.

